data.description: back on market Buyer failed. Welcome home  1 bed 1 full bath, 1ST FLOOR condo inside a gated community! NEW  AC, NEW CARPET and NEW flooring in bathroom and kitchen !!! Kitchen has all white appliances, newer washer and dryer. Outdoor patio has upgraded sliding glass windows!! Assigned covered carport parking with guest parking. Amazing community features include: community clubhouse, pool/spa, fitness center, BBQ area and playground, separate men and women saunas, park w/ trail. Located just minutes away from various shopping centers, gas stations, dining, schools, gyms, and a movie theatre. Access to US-95 just two streets over!! Just 15 minutes away from the strip!!!
